genresAdvancedInfo.name: fado de coimbra
genresAdvancedInfo.description: "Fado de Coimbra" is a traditional Portuguese music genre that originated in the city of Coimbra. It is characterized by the use of acoustic guitars and male vocals, which often tell stories of love, loss, and nostalgia. The music is melancholic and emotional, with a strong emphasis on the lyrics.
